970
00:38:19,699 --> 00:38:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] u istinu se pojavio negdje tamo

971
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] u to jedno vrijeme

972
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] na prelazu ovoga iz Novog,

973
00:38:29,619 --> 00:38:32,219
[SPEAKER_00] mi te kažemo prije Krista,

974
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] poslije Kristal zapravo ima onaj naziv

975
00:38:34,639 --> 00:38:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] prije Nove ere i ovoga,

976
00:38:36,559 --> 00:38:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] poslije Nove ere,

977
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:40,320
[SPEAKER_00] dakle da je u istinu,

978
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] ja pretpostavljam da je vrlo lako moguće

979
00:38:44,119 --> 00:38:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] ta osoba bila tamo,

980
00:38:45,659 --> 00:38:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne bi nastalo sve to što je nastalo,

981
00:38:48,119 --> 00:38:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] dakle s ono što mi znamo kao Novi Zavijet

982
00:38:50,159 --> 00:38:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] i ono što znamo kao i one,

983
00:38:52,159 --> 00:38:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] oni dijelovi,

984
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] oni tekstovi koji nisu ušli u Novi Zavijet,

985
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:59,480
[SPEAKER_00] dakle Novi Zavijet je samo jedan manji paket,

986
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] puno je toga više napisano,

987
00:39:01,500 --> 00:39:03,820
[SPEAKER_00] samo jednostavno nije ušlo ono što bi se nazvalo kanon.

988
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Postoje neki zapisi

989
00:39:06,099 --> 00:39:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi zapravo dali nas lutiti da je u istinu

990
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] postao

991
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:14,739
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa recimo kod Josipa Flavija,

992
00:39:14,739 --> 00:39:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] tog zapravo židovskog povisničara

993
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji je za vrijeme židovskog ustaka

994
00:39:20,079 --> 00:39:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] se zapravo de facto romanizirao recimo to tako,

995
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] jer su rimljani pobjedili,

996
00:39:25,260 --> 00:39:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] nije baš nimao ni pretjerano izbor.

997
00:39:28,380 --> 00:39:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet,

998
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] to može biti dokaz

999
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] da on u istinu postoje.

1000
00:39:34,239 --> 00:39:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pravo pitanje je

1001
00:39:37,119 --> 00:39:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] kakav je on bio,

1002
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] to mi znamo ako vjerujemo

1003
00:39:42,019 --> 00:39:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] u Novi Zavijet.

1004
00:39:44,599 --> 00:39:47,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nam opet Novi Zavijet je samo nekakva vrsta

1005
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] povijesnog izvora,

1006
00:39:48,539 --> 00:39:51,639
[SPEAKER_00] moguće da bi bio posve drugačiji,

1007
00:39:51,639 --> 00:39:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] jer rekao sve one riječi koje je rekao.

1008
00:39:55,159 --> 00:39:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] To je sad veliko pitanje.

1009
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] S obzirom da je vriječ o

1010
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] sinu Božjem,

1011
00:40:00,199 --> 00:40:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] ako ćemo,

1012
00:40:00,699 --> 00:40:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] pari se tako govori,

1013
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] onda u tom mislim da tu više nije pitanje,

1014
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] čak ni toliko povijesti.

1015
00:40:07,239 --> 00:40:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je pitanje vjerovanja.

1016
00:40:09,199 --> 00:40:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ključno pitanje je

1017
00:40:10,079 --> 00:40:11,719
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujete li vi da je on bio ili nije?

1018
00:40:11,719 --> 00:40:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je li on bio ili ne?

1019
00:40:13,519 --> 00:40:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] Krajnjoj liniji,

1020
00:40:14,219 --> 00:40:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] čak mislim da nije ni toliko bitno.

1021
00:40:17,739 --> 00:40:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] zato što

1022
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] čak recimo da vi kažete

1023
00:40:21,179 --> 00:40:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] nije postao.

1024
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Šta to znači ljudima koji vjeruju da je postao?

1025
00:40:24,619 --> 00:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

1026
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:26,679
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da postoji velika razlika

1027
00:40:26,679 --> 00:40:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] između toga da potvrdiš da je neko postao

1028
00:40:29,019 --> 00:40:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na to da je on sin Božji.

1029
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, kažem,

1030
00:40:33,179 --> 00:40:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] oma je stvar vjerovanja

1031
00:40:34,539 --> 00:40:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] i kad je u pitanju vjerovanja

1032
00:40:36,679 --> 00:40:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedan posve drugačiji paket i pristup.

1033
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, tu nema,

1034
00:40:41,900 --> 00:40:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] u vjerovanju nema dokaza.

1035
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] Vi vjerujete ili ne vjerujete.

1036
00:40:45,860 --> 00:40:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ako morate dokazivati ni u pitanju vjera.

1037
00:40:48,019 --> 00:40:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] To je ključ cijele priče.

1038
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i kažem, sa Isusom Kristom

1039
00:40:52,159 --> 00:40:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] definitivno, kako da kažem,

1040
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi bilo svega onoga što se dogodilo.

1041
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da je on izmišljena osoba.

1042
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] Jer jednostavno, previše je toga,

1043
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] previše se toga dogodilo.

1044
00:41:04,699 --> 00:41:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

1045
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] je li Isus Krist,

1046
00:41:08,159 --> 00:41:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] onaj kojeg mi sad znamo

1047
00:41:11,380 --> 00:41:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] iz Pravije iz Novog Zavijeta,

1048
00:41:12,860 --> 00:41:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] jednak onome koji je bio

1049
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] ili je u pitanju,

1050
00:41:15,579 --> 00:41:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] to je sad pitanje na koje isto se pokušava odgovorit

1051
00:41:19,639 --> 00:41:20,659
[SPEAKER_00] o ho-ho godina.

1052
00:41:20,659 --> 00:41:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem,

1053
00:41:21,239 --> 00:41:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali na kraju se sve svodi u pitanje vjerovanja.

1054
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] Vi imate

1055
00:41:26,159 --> 00:41:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] niz knjiga koji su napisane,

1056
00:41:28,539 --> 00:41:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] koji su pokušavale odgovorit

1057
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to moguće bilo,

1058
00:41:32,059 --> 00:41:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] kako je krenula

1059
00:41:32,940 --> 00:41:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo ta

1060
00:41:34,139 --> 00:41:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] nova sljedba unutar židovstva.

1061
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Isus je bio židov.

1062
00:41:40,039 --> 00:41:42,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su sve židovi oko njega.

1063
00:41:42,039 --> 00:41:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] Apostoli su židovi.

1064
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali ta nova vjera koja dolazi,

1065
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:52,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja je sad rasprava koja će se voditi o ho-ho?

1066
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:53,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim,

1067
00:41:53,239 --> 00:41:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] tu nema po meni nekakvog odgovora

1068
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] koji bi bio definitivno povisničarski.

1069
00:42:00,179 --> 00:42:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jer u tom slučaju,

1070
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] kažem,

1071
00:42:01,679 --> 00:42:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] čak ni to,

1072
00:42:02,559 --> 00:42:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam sklon tvrditi da,

1073
00:42:04,619 --> 00:42:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujem da je u istinu se to,

1074
00:42:06,420 --> 00:42:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] da je postoje,

1075
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne bi se dogodilo sve ovo.

1076
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] A sad ovaj dio,

1077
00:42:11,699 --> 00:42:13,139
[SPEAKER_00] sin Boži,

1078
00:42:13,139 --> 00:42:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] sve to trojstvo,

1079
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] čuda.

1080
00:42:15,719 --> 00:42:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] To je pitanje vjere.

1081
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] To već nije pitanje dokaza.

1082
00:42:19,119 --> 00:42:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] To da li je se nešto dogodilo,

1083
00:42:21,940 --> 00:42:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] to već isključivo ima veze sa vjerom,

1084
00:42:26,619 --> 00:42:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] a teško da ima veze sa dokazom,

1085
00:42:28,699 --> 00:42:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer, kažem,

1086
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] tu čak i pitanje dokaza nije ni relevantno.

1087
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je jednostavno izašlo izvan povijesti

1088
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] i postalo vjera.

1089
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to odmah na jednoj drugoj razini,

1090
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] kažem?

1091
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] Je, čini mi se recimo Mahatma Gandhi

1092
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:45,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji je živio u nedavnoj povijesti,

1093
00:42:45,300 --> 00:42:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] za njega možemo reći da je živio,

1094
00:42:49,719 --> 00:42:51,679
[SPEAKER_01] da je bio živa osoba,

1095
00:42:51,679 --> 00:42:53,980
[SPEAKER_01] i postoje neki dokaze.

1096
00:42:53,980 --> 00:42:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, danas uz ovu umjetnu inteligenciju

1097
00:42:56,019 --> 00:42:57,519
[SPEAKER_01] i sve te stvari koje se događuje,

1098
00:42:58,320 --> 00:42:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] sve je teže i teže,

1099
00:42:59,300 --> 00:43:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] razaznati šta je istina, šta nije,

1100
00:43:01,940 --> 00:43:02,860
[SPEAKER_01] šta je realno, šta nije,

1101
00:43:02,860 --> 00:43:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne ulazimo sad u tu duboku filozofiju.

1102
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je tu pitanje, opet kažem,

1103
00:43:06,380 --> 00:43:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedan paket,

1104
00:43:07,599 --> 00:43:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad uđe vjera u sve,

1105
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] onda su stvari drugačije.

1106
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] Misliš religija zapravo?

1107
00:43:12,719 --> 00:43:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, da.

1108
00:43:13,239 --> 00:43:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je ona jedna sjajna scena iz filma,

1109
00:43:17,539 --> 00:43:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, krvavjerik, da, od Monty Pythona,

1110
00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] kad zapravo oni idu prema Valhali,

1111
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] oni su vikinzi,

1112
00:43:25,659 --> 00:43:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] oni idu prema Valhali,

1113
00:43:27,260 --> 00:43:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] i s njima je jedan redovnik,

1114
00:43:28,699 --> 00:43:30,280
[SPEAKER_00] koji ih pokušava bezuspješno

1115
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] na kršćanstvo preobratiti,

1116
00:43:34,300 --> 00:43:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] i sad uglavnom u jednom trenutku

1117
00:43:35,659 --> 00:43:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] oni plove, plove,

1118
00:43:36,539 --> 00:43:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] i svi vikinzi vide ispred sebe Valhalu

1119
00:43:38,739 --> 00:43:41,860
[SPEAKER_00] sa dvo vratima ogromnim

1120
00:43:41,860 --> 00:43:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] i sad svi viču Valhala,

1121
00:43:43,500 --> 00:43:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] jedino taj redovnik gleda i kaže

1122
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] što vi vidite, ja ne vidim ništa.

1123
00:43:46,579 --> 00:43:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] To je to pitanje.

1124
00:43:48,980 --> 00:43:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] To su dvije rezine.

1125
00:43:50,139 --> 00:43:52,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, jedni vjeruju u to da postoji Valhala

1126
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:55,679
[SPEAKER_00] i da unutra ratnici se tuku

1127
00:43:55,679 --> 00:43:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] od jutra do mraka,

1128
00:43:56,639 --> 00:43:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] piju medovinu i uživaju u svom životu,

1129
00:43:59,579 --> 00:44:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] drugi misle da ne vidi ništa,

1130
00:44:01,119 --> 00:44:01,940
[SPEAKER_00] vidi samo more.

1131
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je ovdje.

1132
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:05,639
[SPEAKER_00] Vjera, religija,

1133
00:44:05,639 --> 00:44:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] tiže stvari na jednu drugu razinu.

1134
00:44:08,460 --> 00:44:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je, mi možemo raspravljati

1135
00:44:10,360 --> 00:44:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] o rimskom carstvu na prilazu

1136
00:44:12,119 --> 00:44:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] i stare u novo eru,

1137
00:44:13,280 --> 00:44:14,940
[SPEAKER_00] mi možemo razgovarati o tome

1138
00:44:14,940 --> 00:44:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je Poncije Pilat

1139
00:44:16,860 --> 00:44:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] dopremio munjevitu legiju

1140
00:44:18,880 --> 00:44:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje,

1141
00:44:19,599 --> 00:44:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji su bili neredi

1142
00:44:20,719 --> 00:44:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerojatno u tom neredu

1143
00:44:22,900 --> 00:44:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] ona priča o tome

1144
00:44:24,579 --> 00:44:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] da su se rimljeni bojali nereda,

1145
00:44:26,059 --> 00:44:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] a onda i nakon toga je židavska zajednica

1146
00:44:27,840 --> 00:44:30,119
[SPEAKER_00] što će rimljeni napraviti zbog tog nereda.

1147
00:44:30,119 --> 00:44:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to vjerojatno stoji

1148
00:44:31,199 --> 00:44:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] i to je napravljeno.

1149
00:44:32,019 --> 00:44:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovaj dio

1150
00:44:32,940 --> 00:44:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus Krist, kojeg mi znamo,

1151
00:44:36,059 --> 00:44:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] to više nije stvar povijesti.

1152
00:44:37,559 --> 00:44:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] To jednostavno izlazi iz

1153
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] povijesne rasprave

1154
00:44:42,199 --> 00:44:43,280
[SPEAKER_00] i postoje dio vjere.

1155
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je već drugi paket.

1156
00:44:44,780 --> 00:44:47,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna od fascinantnijih knjiga

1157
00:44:47,780 --> 00:44:48,920
[SPEAKER_01] koju sam pročitao

1158
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] u toj kategoriji povijesti

1159
00:44:51,159 --> 00:44:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] mi je

1160
00:44:53,260 --> 00:44:54,980
[SPEAKER_01] Lessons of History,

1161
00:44:54,980 --> 00:44:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] lekcije povijesti,

1162
00:44:56,460 --> 00:44:59,739
[SPEAKER_01] autori Will i Ariel Durant.

1163
00:44:59,739 --> 00:45:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] jeste čuli za njih,

1164
00:45:01,019 --> 00:45:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] ste čitali to.

1165
00:45:01,679 --> 00:45:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] Čuo sam za njih,

1166
00:45:02,719 --> 00:45:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] ali nisam čital.

1167
00:45:03,639 --> 00:45:05,300
[SPEAKER_01] Fascinantna knjiga.

1168
00:45:05,300 --> 00:45:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan od razloga zašto je meni fascinantna,

