01:05:26,360 --> 01:05:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] koje su bile

2063
01:05:26,880 --> 01:05:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] zadane

2064
01:05:27,440 --> 01:05:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] hladnim oružjem

2065
01:05:28,460 --> 01:05:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili strelicama.

2066
01:05:29,300 --> 01:05:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

2067
01:05:29,699 --> 01:05:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] nije u pitanju

2068
01:05:30,380 --> 01:05:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da je netko

2069
01:05:31,400 --> 01:05:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] umro pri jednom smrću

2070
01:05:32,420 --> 01:05:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] ili da ste

2071
01:05:32,780 --> 01:05:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] ubili jednog

2072
01:05:33,380 --> 01:05:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] ili dvoje

2073
01:05:33,880 --> 01:05:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego ste imali

2074
01:05:34,880 --> 01:05:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] unutra

2075
01:05:35,199 --> 01:05:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] masovnu grobnicu

2076
01:05:36,059 --> 01:05:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je bilo

2077
01:05:36,360 --> 01:05:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] bačeno

2078
01:05:36,679 --> 01:05:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] trideset,

2079
01:05:37,039 --> 01:05:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] četardeset

2080
01:05:37,579 --> 01:05:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] tijela.

2081
01:05:37,780 --> 01:05:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

2082
01:05:38,039 --> 01:05:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je nešto

2083
01:05:38,599 --> 01:05:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] što

2084
01:05:38,920 --> 01:05:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] postoji

2085
01:05:40,739 --> 01:05:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] dosta dugo.

2086
01:05:41,440 --> 01:05:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je do toga

2087
01:05:44,199 --> 01:05:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] došlo odgovora?

2088
01:05:44,860 --> 01:05:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno,

2089
01:05:45,280 --> 01:05:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] nema,

2090
01:05:45,659 --> 01:05:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo mi znati

2091
01:05:46,440 --> 01:05:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ljudi ratuju

2092
01:05:47,360 --> 01:05:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] to odgovor koji

2093
01:05:48,579 --> 01:05:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne možemo ga dati.

2094
01:05:51,480 --> 01:05:52,179
[SPEAKER_00] To je jednostavno

2095
01:05:52,179 --> 01:05:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] tako.

2096
01:05:52,599 --> 01:05:54,739
[SPEAKER_00] Problem sa ratom je

2097
01:05:54,739 --> 01:05:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] što je on,

2098
01:05:55,960 --> 01:05:56,719
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god da to

2099
01:05:56,719 --> 01:05:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] grubo zvuče,

2100
01:05:59,119 --> 01:06:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] dugo vremena

2101
01:06:00,360 --> 01:06:01,800
[SPEAKER_00] smatan rješenjem.

2102
01:06:01,800 --> 01:06:03,800
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji

2103
01:06:03,800 --> 01:06:05,659
[SPEAKER_00] Hugo Grossius,

2104
01:06:05,659 --> 01:06:06,679
[SPEAKER_00] jedan nizozemski

2105
01:06:06,679 --> 01:06:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] pravnik,

2106
01:06:07,380 --> 01:06:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] smatrao ga zapravo

2107
01:06:08,579 --> 01:06:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] ocem međunarodnog prava.

2108
01:06:10,380 --> 01:06:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] I on je

2109
01:06:11,800 --> 01:06:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] u tim jednim

2110
01:06:12,659 --> 01:06:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] svojim dijelima

2111
01:06:13,300 --> 01:06:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo

2112
01:06:13,840 --> 01:06:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] pojednostavljujem

2113
01:06:15,059 --> 01:06:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] naravno

2114
01:06:15,559 --> 01:06:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] zbog

2115
01:06:16,219 --> 01:06:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] priče,

2116
01:06:17,920 --> 01:06:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali

2117
01:06:18,159 --> 01:06:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] je utemeljeno

2118
01:06:19,159 --> 01:06:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] o njegovim knjigama

2119
01:06:19,980 --> 01:06:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] priča je da ovako.

2120
01:06:21,699 --> 01:06:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vi i ja smo

2121
01:06:22,860 --> 01:06:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] privatni građani.

2122
01:06:24,039 --> 01:06:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sporimo se

2123
01:06:25,079 --> 01:06:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] oko

2124
01:06:25,539 --> 01:06:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga stola.

2125
01:06:26,960 --> 01:06:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem da je

2126
01:06:28,739 --> 01:06:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] on moj,

2127
01:06:29,480 --> 01:06:30,460
[SPEAKER_00] vi kažete da je vaš.

2128
01:06:30,460 --> 01:06:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ko će razriješiti spor?

2129
01:06:32,679 --> 01:06:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo se potući,

2130
01:06:34,699 --> 01:06:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nije civilizirano

2131
01:06:36,159 --> 01:06:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] i objektivno

2132
01:06:37,079 --> 01:06:38,159
[SPEAKER_00] to nije ni dopušteno,

2133
01:06:38,159 --> 01:06:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] već u njegovo vrijeme.

2134
01:06:39,079 --> 01:06:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] Što imamo,

2135
01:06:40,300 --> 01:06:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćemo znat

2136
01:06:41,139 --> 01:06:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] čije stolo tići ćemo

2137
01:06:42,579 --> 01:06:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] na sud?

2138
01:06:43,039 --> 01:06:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljev sud,

2139
01:06:44,739 --> 01:06:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] gradski sud,

2140
01:06:45,519 --> 01:06:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] kakav god.

2141
01:06:46,119 --> 01:06:47,800
[SPEAKER_00] I na sudu ćemo

2142
01:06:47,800 --> 01:06:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] predstaviti

2143
01:06:48,519 --> 01:06:49,780
[SPEAKER_00] svoj slučaj,

2144
01:06:49,780 --> 01:06:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] podasrit nekakve dokaze

2145
01:06:52,719 --> 01:06:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] i sudac će reći

2146
01:06:54,079 --> 01:06:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] stol je vaš.

2147
01:06:55,380 --> 01:06:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to mogu prihvatiti

2148
01:06:58,079 --> 01:06:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne,

2149
01:06:58,360 --> 01:06:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne prihvatiti

2150
01:06:59,099 --> 01:07:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] mogu se opet potući,

2151
01:07:00,059 --> 01:07:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] što je opet kaznano dijelo,

2152
01:07:01,219 --> 01:07:02,760
[SPEAKER_00] nepriznavanje suda,

2153
01:07:02,760 --> 01:07:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] svimo tamo

2154
01:07:03,519 --> 01:07:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] i riješili smo stvar.

2155
01:07:04,840 --> 01:07:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se dvije države

2156
01:07:07,539 --> 01:07:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] sukobljavaju

2157
01:07:09,219 --> 01:07:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] oko komada

2158
01:07:10,420 --> 01:07:11,320
[SPEAKER_00] zemlje,

2159
01:07:11,320 --> 01:07:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] neke doline,

2160
01:07:12,260 --> 01:07:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je sud

2161
01:07:14,400 --> 01:07:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji će riješiti

2162
01:07:15,440 --> 01:07:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] taj spor?

2163
01:07:17,139 --> 01:07:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] nema ga.

2164
01:07:17,780 --> 01:07:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nema ga.

2165
01:07:17,880 --> 01:07:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] I onda oni riješavaju

2166
01:07:20,960 --> 01:07:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] ratom.

2167
01:07:21,460 --> 01:07:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] Trave se sa vojskama

2168
01:07:23,960 --> 01:07:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ovo bilo moje.

2169
01:07:25,079 --> 01:07:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa novo,

2170
01:07:28,039 --> 01:07:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] nisam nekao,

2171
01:07:28,719 --> 01:07:29,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad kažem da je dobar dio

2172
01:07:29,760 --> 01:07:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] povijesti,

2173
01:07:30,260 --> 01:07:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] sukob oko nekretnina,

2174
01:07:31,599 --> 01:07:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] kako bi rekao

2175
01:07:32,400 --> 01:07:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] narednik u tankoj crvenoj liniji,

2176
01:07:34,159 --> 01:07:34,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad on

2177
01:07:34,679 --> 01:07:36,099
[SPEAKER_00] silazi s onog brda,

2178
01:07:36,219 --> 01:07:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je američka vojska

2179
01:07:37,539 --> 01:07:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] pokušava to brdo otet

2180
01:07:38,960 --> 01:07:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] od japanske vojske,

2181
01:07:40,940 --> 01:07:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] onda ona nako silazi

2182
01:07:42,139 --> 01:07:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] bježeći od metaka

2183
01:07:43,519 --> 01:07:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] i obraća se svojim vojnicima

2184
01:07:44,760 --> 01:07:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

2185
01:07:45,079 --> 01:07:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] cijela ova stvar je

2186
01:07:46,480 --> 01:07:47,219
[SPEAKER_00] zbog nekretnina.

2187
01:07:47,219 --> 01:07:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Je li naša i mi nije?

2188
01:07:49,659 --> 01:07:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] Problem je,

2189
01:07:52,039 --> 01:07:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] što kažem,

2190
01:07:52,880 --> 01:07:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] je rat, nažalost,

2191
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:55,219
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek bio odgovor.

2192
01:07:55,219 --> 01:07:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, nije bio odgovor

2193
01:07:56,320 --> 01:07:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] za ljude koji su ginuli unutra

2194
01:07:57,780 --> 01:07:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] da su mogli pomoći,

2195
01:07:59,199 --> 01:07:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno ne bi.

2196
01:07:59,880 --> 01:08:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kada su u pitanju

2197
01:08:02,079 --> 01:08:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji imaju mogućnost

2198
01:08:04,480 --> 01:08:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] podić vojske,

2199
01:08:06,219 --> 01:08:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] i oni koji kranjuli

2200
01:08:07,800 --> 01:08:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] imaju mogućnosti

2201
01:08:08,960 --> 01:08:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] namaknuti novce

2202
01:08:10,099 --> 01:08:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] da bi te vojske hranili

2203
01:08:11,440 --> 01:08:12,360
[SPEAKER_00] i plaćali,

2204
01:08:12,360 --> 01:08:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] rat je uvijek bio odgovor.

2205
01:08:14,400 --> 01:08:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] On je tu bio negdje.

2206
01:08:15,619 --> 01:08:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] To ne znači da ljudi

2207
01:08:16,579 --> 01:08:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] nisu bili svjesni

2208
01:08:17,500 --> 01:08:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] da je rat loš,

2209
01:08:18,119 --> 01:08:19,399
[SPEAKER_00] kažem, od Grka nadalje.

2210
01:08:19,399 --> 01:08:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] Od srednjem vijeku

2211
01:08:21,859 --> 01:08:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] katolička crkva

2212
01:08:23,699 --> 01:08:24,479
[SPEAKER_00] je pokušavala

2213
01:08:24,479 --> 01:08:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] kroz dane u tjednu

2214
01:08:25,840 --> 01:08:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] odrediti kad se

2215
01:08:26,840 --> 01:08:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] kao ne bi trebalo ratovati

2216
01:08:28,239 --> 01:08:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] da bi spriječila mogućnost,

2217
01:08:29,640 --> 01:08:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] naravno ne može se ratovati

2218
01:08:30,640 --> 01:08:31,479
[SPEAKER_00] na određene svece,

2219
01:08:31,479 --> 01:08:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] na određene blagdane,

2220
01:08:32,399 --> 01:08:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda su pokušali

2221
01:08:33,539 --> 01:08:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] i dane u tjednu odrediti.

2222
01:08:34,920 --> 01:08:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kako bi se smanjilo?

2223
01:08:36,460 --> 01:08:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nije se, naravno, prihvatilo.

2224
01:08:38,720 --> 01:08:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što je rat,

2225
01:08:40,779 --> 01:08:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god da bili grubi,

2226
01:08:42,579 --> 01:08:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] smatran kao rješenje.

2227
01:08:44,619 --> 01:08:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Neke stvari ćemo rješiti.

2228
01:08:47,000 --> 01:08:48,399
[SPEAKER_00] Smatramo da je ovo naše,

2229
01:08:48,399 --> 01:08:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] smatramo da ne želimo dati ovo,

2230
01:08:52,319 --> 01:08:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] suko bi oko nečega.

2231
01:08:53,640 --> 01:08:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] Rat, to da rat je

2232
01:08:56,439 --> 01:08:59,359
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što bi trebalo izbjegavati,

2233
01:08:59,359 --> 01:09:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] je, kažem, novovjekovna priča.

2234
01:09:01,380 --> 01:09:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] To je 20. stoljeće,

2235
01:09:02,720 --> 01:09:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] Kellogg-Briandov,

2236
01:09:04,319 --> 01:09:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] takozvani pakt,

2237
01:09:05,319 --> 01:09:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, američki ministrovanski poslao Kellogg,

2238
01:09:07,819 --> 01:09:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] francuski ministrovanski poslao Briand,

2239
01:09:09,760 --> 01:09:12,060
[SPEAKER_00] uviti su prvi koji pokušavaju

2240
01:09:12,060 --> 01:09:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] napraviti

2241
01:09:12,760 --> 01:09:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] međunarodni okvir

2242
01:09:14,920 --> 01:09:16,060
[SPEAKER_00] gdje bi zapravo

2243
01:09:16,060 --> 01:09:18,279
[SPEAKER_00] rat bio stavljen izvan snage

2244
01:09:18,279 --> 01:09:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] ili barem dobro reguliran.

2245
01:09:20,460 --> 01:09:22,859
[SPEAKER_00] I gdje bi agresivni rad

2246
01:09:22,859 --> 01:09:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] bio kažnjiv.

2247
01:09:23,699 --> 01:09:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je, recimo, ovo što danas imamo,

2248
01:09:27,000 --> 01:09:28,779
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo da se agresivni rad smatra

2249
01:09:28,779 --> 01:09:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] teškim zločinom, prekršenjem međunarodnog prava.

2250
01:09:32,460 --> 01:09:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Magresivni ratovi u 19. stoljeću su,

2251
01:09:35,960 --> 01:09:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, naravno da,

2252
01:09:37,739 --> 01:09:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] ako biste vi iznenada i bez opravdanja

2253
01:09:40,460 --> 01:09:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] napali nekog, da vam je to zapravo

2254
01:09:42,119 --> 01:09:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek bilo riskantno,

2255
01:09:43,380 --> 01:09:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo ako biste taj rat izgubili,

2256
01:09:45,920 --> 01:09:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali niste imali ovaj pravni okvir

2257
01:09:47,619 --> 01:09:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji danas, recimo, imate da biste

2258
01:09:49,239 --> 01:09:52,220
[SPEAKER_00] kažnjavali agresiju ili to da vi

2259
01:09:52,220 --> 01:09:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] spori između dvije države

2260
01:09:54,340 --> 01:09:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] krenete rješavati na vojsko.

2261
01:09:57,220 --> 01:09:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] Danas se smatra da to jednostavno nije prihvatljivo.

2262
01:09:59,579 --> 01:10:00,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kažem, to je novija stvar.

2263
01:10:00,739 --> 01:10:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] To jedva da je starije od jednog stoljeća.

2264
01:10:04,140 --> 01:10:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] I opet ste imali ljude, povijesničare,

2265
01:10:06,220 --> 01:10:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] istraživače međunarodnih odnosa,

2266
01:10:08,359 --> 01:10:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji su rekli da to suludo zabraniti rat.

2267
01:10:10,680 --> 01:10:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, to je to kod da pokušavate nešto,

2268
01:10:12,859 --> 01:10:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] nešto, zabraniti disanje.

2269
01:10:14,699 --> 01:10:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, i to vidimo iz naše povijesti,

2270
01:10:18,319 --> 01:10:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god da mi smatrali da je rat grozan,

2271
01:10:20,699 --> 01:10:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] da nije način rješavanja bilo kakvog problema,

2272
01:10:26,260 --> 01:10:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] da je čak u zadnje stoljeće još nešto

2273
01:10:30,199 --> 01:10:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] se smatra kao nečim pogotovo agresivni,

2274
01:10:32,979 --> 01:10:34,640
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne bi smijelo naditi

2275
01:10:34,640 --> 01:10:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebalo biti kažnjivo prema međunarodnom pravu

2276
01:10:37,279 --> 01:10:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] i da bi to trebalo biti ratni zločin.

2277
01:10:38,739 --> 01:10:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] Svejedno imate ratova koliko hoćete u ovom trenutku

2278
01:10:42,739 --> 01:10:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] dok mi govorimo.

2279
01:10:43,539 --> 01:10:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je to naravno tako odvešće nas,

2280
01:10:47,579 --> 01:10:50,119
[SPEAKER_00] odvelo bi nas u ne znam nija dokud,

2281
01:10:50,119 --> 01:10:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali kažem opet ja ono što mogu reći

2282
01:10:53,180 --> 01:10:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] je da je rat jako dugo sa nama

2283
01:10:55,380 --> 01:10:57,439
[SPEAKER_00] i da će jako dugo i ostati sa nama.

2284
01:10:57,439 --> 01:11:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, ništa nije bolje od tog

2285
01:11:01,819 --> 01:11:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] što ja to kažem

2286
01:11:03,220 --> 01:11:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] i što sam siguran da sam, nažalost,

2287
01:11:05,359 --> 01:11:06,600
[SPEAKER_00] po tom pitanju u pravu,

2288
01:11:06,600 --> 01:11:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] ali jedino što tu može pomoći

2289
01:11:10,060 --> 01:11:12,239
[SPEAKER_00] je ustrajan rad na tome

2290
01:11:12,239 --> 01:11:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se ono što je moguće više ograniči

2291
01:11:14,159 --> 01:11:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] i da se zapravo kazni,

2292
01:11:15,659 --> 01:11:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] pokuša kazniti,

2293
01:11:17,340 --> 01:11:19,479
[SPEAKER_00] barem agresivni rat.

2294
01:11:19,479 --> 01:11:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to da vi smatrate

2295
01:11:21,739 --> 01:11:24,340
[SPEAKER_00] da neke stvari možete riješiti

2296
01:11:24,340 --> 01:11:25,520
[SPEAKER_00] napadom na drugu zemlju.

2297
01:11:25,520 --> 01:11:27,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet kažem,

2298
01:11:27,439 --> 01:11:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] ima ratova sad

2299
01:11:30,199 --> 01:11:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji su očito agresivni,

2300
01:11:33,239 --> 01:11:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa tko ih je kaznio.

2301
01:11:34,460 --> 01:11:35,140
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju, nažalost,

2302
01:11:35,140 --> 01:11:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost, sve će pokazati se

2303
01:11:36,539 --> 01:11:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] na bojnom polju.

2304
01:11:37,239 --> 01:11:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] A bojno polje nije pravedno.

2305
01:11:39,340 --> 01:11:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] Njemu pobjeđuje najjači,

2306
01:11:40,960 --> 01:11:42,020
[SPEAKER_00] ne one koji ima pravo.

2307
01:11:42,020 --> 01:11:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro je kad najjači

2308
01:11:45,159 --> 01:11:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] je ujedno i u pravu,

2309
01:11:46,699 --> 01:11:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali često puta tako nije.

2310
01:11:50,420 --> 01:11:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da li postoji uopće rat

2311
01:11:51,579 --> 01:11:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] koji nije agresivan rat?

2312
01:11:52,739 --> 01:11:54,600
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je ono što se smatra

2313
01:11:54,600 --> 01:11:55,399
[SPEAKER_00] obrambeni rat.

2314
01:11:55,399 --> 01:11:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, recimo,

2315
01:11:56,279 --> 01:11:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali to opet pitanje

2316
01:11:57,279 --> 01:11:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] koga vodi.

2317
01:11:58,000 --> 01:11:59,199
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi sad razgovaramo

2318
01:11:59,199 --> 01:11:59,699
[SPEAKER_00] o ratu, naravno.

2319
01:11:59,699 --> 01:12:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] Rat je zapravo da se krim

2320
01:12:01,319 --> 01:12:02,439
[SPEAKER_01] malo, gružno izrazi,

2321
01:12:02,439 --> 01:12:03,060
[SPEAKER_01] kao ples.

2322
01:12:03,060 --> 01:12:03,899
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, potrebne su

2323
01:12:03,899 --> 01:12:04,699
[SPEAKER_01] bije strane, jel?

2324
01:12:04,699 --> 01:12:05,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ali recimo,

2325
01:12:05,479 --> 01:12:08,020
[SPEAKER_00] obrambeni rat nije.

2326
01:12:08,020 --> 01:12:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Smatra se,

2327
01:12:08,960 --> 01:12:09,720
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

2328
01:12:09,720 --> 01:12:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] kao što svako ima pravo

2329
01:12:11,640 --> 01:12:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] na samoobranu

2330
01:12:12,420 --> 01:12:13,560
[SPEAKER_00] i država ima pravo

2331
01:12:13,560 --> 01:12:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] na samoobranu.

2332
01:12:14,359 --> 01:12:17,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet kažem,

2333
01:12:17,899 --> 01:12:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] i u tom obrambenom ratu

2334
01:12:19,279 --> 01:12:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] stradaće ljudi.

2335
01:12:20,159 --> 01:12:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] I u tom obrambenom ratu

2336
01:12:21,520 --> 01:12:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] se mora ubijet.

2337
01:12:22,500 --> 01:12:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] U tom obrambenom ratu

2338
01:12:23,539 --> 01:12:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] se mora pobjediti protivnik.

2339
01:12:24,840 --> 01:12:26,560
[SPEAKER_00] Pobjediti protivnika

2340
01:12:26,560 --> 01:12:27,600
[SPEAKER_00] ne možete na ta najčina

2341
01:12:27,600 --> 01:12:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] da mu dokažete

2342
01:12:28,300 --> 01:12:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] da je on u krivu.

2343
01:12:29,600 --> 01:12:30,979
[SPEAKER_00] Nema dživu džicuva u ratu.

2344
01:12:30,979 --> 01:12:32,020
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost,

2345
01:12:32,020 --> 01:12:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] to nije kao borba mačaka

2346
01:12:33,720 --> 01:12:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili džudo

2347
01:12:34,539 --> 01:12:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] gdje vi u dva, tri poteza

2348
01:12:35,939 --> 01:12:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] riješite stvari.

2349
01:12:36,800 --> 01:12:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] To traje godinama.

2350
01:12:38,079 --> 01:12:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] I neki put desetljećima

2351
01:12:39,600 --> 01:12:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] i neki put stoljećima.

2352
01:12:40,819 --> 01:12:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

2353
01:12:42,500 --> 01:12:44,060
[SPEAKER_00] ne bez razloga

2354
01:12:44,060 --> 01:12:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] mi govorimo

2355
01:12:44,500 --> 01:12:45,560
[SPEAKER_00] o stogodišnjem ratu

2356
01:12:45,560 --> 01:12:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] između Engleske i Francuske

2357
01:12:46,819 --> 01:12:47,520
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

2358
01:12:47,520 --> 01:12:48,640
[SPEAKER_00] Povijesti Rima

2359
01:12:48,640 --> 01:12:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] godine nije bilo

2360
01:12:51,000 --> 01:12:52,039
[SPEAKER_00] kada oni nisu ratovali.

2361
01:12:52,039 --> 01:12:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost,

2362
01:12:53,840 --> 01:12:54,600
[SPEAKER_00] to je tako.

2363
01:12:54,600 --> 01:12:55,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem,

2364
01:12:55,180 --> 01:12:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] odgovor,

2365
01:12:55,840 --> 01:12:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je to tako?

2366
01:12:57,239 --> 01:12:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudska priroda

2367
01:12:57,880 --> 01:12:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] smo tamo odberu

2368
01:12:58,739 --> 01:12:59,399
[SPEAKER_00] nas daleko.

2369
01:12:59,399 --> 01:13:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se zadovoljavam

2370
01:13:01,500 --> 01:13:02,300
[SPEAKER_00] konstatacijom

2371
01:13:02,300 --> 01:13:02,899
[SPEAKER_00] da je nažalost

2372
01:13:02,899 --> 01:13:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] rat dosta dugo

2373
01:13:03,840 --> 01:13:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] već s nama

2374
01:13:04,359 --> 01:13:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] i da nažalost

2375
01:13:05,239 --> 01:13:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] će i dalje biti.

2376
01:13:06,079 --> 01:13:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] Osim ako se neku čudo

2377
01:13:07,119 --> 01:13:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] ne dogodi.

2378
01:13:07,640 --> 01:13:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Šta kaže povijest?

2379
01:13:09,960 --> 01:13:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] Da li su učestali

2380
01:13:10,779 --> 01:13:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] ratovi sa susjedima

2381
01:13:14,500 --> 01:13:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa susjedi su uvijek problem.

2382
01:13:17,300 --> 01:13:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] Muži, žena će se.

2383
01:13:18,960 --> 01:13:21,100
[SPEAKER_00] Susjedi su uvijek problem.

2384
01:13:21,100 --> 01:13:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, pa zapravo

2385
01:13:23,460 --> 01:13:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] čim igra...

2386
01:13:26,340 --> 01:13:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sve ovisi od ome...

2387
01:13:27,880 --> 01:13:28,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nekretni ne su u pitanju.

2388
01:13:28,920 --> 01:13:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ako postoji spor,

2389
01:13:30,680 --> 01:13:31,600
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ako...

2390
01:13:31,600 --> 01:13:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u istinu postoje

2391
01:13:32,619 --> 01:13:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] zemlje koje nisu ratovali.

2392
01:13:33,819 --> 01:13:34,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet,

2393
01:13:34,840 --> 01:13:36,199
[SPEAKER_00] to znači da su one riješile

2394
01:13:36,199 --> 01:13:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće sporne situacije

2395
01:13:37,859 --> 01:13:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] na miran način

2396
01:13:38,619 --> 01:13:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] ili su nekad davno

2397
01:13:39,500 --> 01:13:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] vodili rat.

2398
01:13:40,079 --> 01:13:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Primjer,

2399
01:13:41,380 --> 01:13:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] Švicarska je danas zemlja

2400
01:13:42,619 --> 01:13:44,479
[SPEAKER_00] koja sigurno u zadnjih...

2401
01:13:44,479 --> 01:13:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, još malo sad će

2402
01:13:45,260 --> 01:13:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Bog mi i dva stoljeća.

2403
01:13:46,779 --> 01:13:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nije ratovala.

2404
01:13:49,319 --> 01:13:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] One živiju miru.

2405
01:13:51,380 --> 01:13:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo žive

2406
01:13:52,699 --> 01:13:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] zajednice,

2407
01:13:54,859 --> 01:13:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] etničke zajednice,

2408
01:13:56,100 --> 01:13:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] a Njemci,

2409
01:13:57,880 --> 01:13:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] Francuzi,

2410
01:13:58,840 --> 01:14:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] Italijani

2411
01:14:00,619 --> 01:14:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] govore različitim jezicima,

2412
01:14:03,380 --> 01:14:05,439
[SPEAKER_00] imaju preko dvadesetak kantona

2413
01:14:05,439 --> 01:14:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] i da ona.

2414
01:14:07,840 --> 01:14:09,020
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je njihova tajna?

2415
01:14:09,020 --> 01:14:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Švicarci su

2416
01:14:11,579 --> 01:14:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] stoljećima se trvili

2417
01:14:14,220 --> 01:14:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] između sebe

2418
01:14:15,079 --> 01:14:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] i izvozili svoje plaćenike

2419
01:14:17,699 --> 01:14:18,939
[SPEAKER_00] po cijelu Evropi.

2420
01:14:18,939 --> 01:14:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bez razloga

2421
01:14:22,539 --> 01:14:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] papina garda

2422
01:14:23,579 --> 01:14:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] su švicarci.

2423
01:14:24,539 --> 01:14:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su papina garda

2424
01:14:26,539 --> 01:14:26,979
[SPEAKER_00] švicarci?

2425
01:14:26,979 --> 01:14:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što su švicarci

2426
01:14:28,000 --> 01:14:28,899
[SPEAKER_00] kada i garda nastala

2427
01:14:28,899 --> 01:14:29,859
[SPEAKER_00] bili najbolji vojnici.

2428
01:14:30,500 --> 01:14:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] kao plaćenici su bili

2429
01:14:31,680 --> 01:14:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatno na glasu

2430
01:14:33,720 --> 01:14:35,819
[SPEAKER_00] kao najprofesionalniji

2431
01:14:35,819 --> 01:14:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] i najubojitiji vojnici.

2432
01:14:37,380 --> 01:14:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] U jednom trenutku

2433
01:14:39,920 --> 01:14:42,560
[SPEAKER_00] da li su se umorili

2434
01:14:42,560 --> 01:14:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] od ubijanja

2435
01:14:43,199 --> 01:14:44,600
[SPEAKER_00] ili su odlučili

2436
01:14:44,600 --> 01:14:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] riješiti svoje stvari,

2437
01:14:45,640 --> 01:14:47,060
[SPEAKER_00] što god da su napravili,

2438
01:14:47,060 --> 01:14:48,600
[SPEAKER_00] zadnja dva stoljeća

2439
01:14:48,600 --> 01:14:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] će se ne trve.

2440
01:14:49,140 --> 01:14:50,439
[SPEAKER_00] Svi ti kantoni,

2441
01:14:50,439 --> 01:14:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] svi te nacije,

2442
01:14:52,119 --> 01:14:53,100
[SPEAKER_00] svi ti jezici.

2443
01:14:53,100 --> 01:14:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] Čak ni internom.

2444
01:14:55,340 --> 01:14:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Oni zapravo ima

2445
01:14:57,420 --> 01:14:58,239
[SPEAKER_00] jednu uređenu

2446
01:14:58,239 --> 01:14:59,720
[SPEAKER_00] državu do duše

2447
01:14:59,720 --> 01:15:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] naravno to postoje

2448
01:15:00,659 --> 01:15:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] onaj grozan citat

2449
01:15:02,000 --> 01:15:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] iz trećeg čovjeka

2450
01:15:03,239 --> 01:15:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] kada Orson Welles

2451
01:15:04,920 --> 01:15:06,479
[SPEAKER_00] negativac kaže

2452
01:15:06,479 --> 01:15:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] isto priča o tome

2453
01:15:08,119 --> 01:15:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] da je rat i sukops

2454
01:15:09,199 --> 01:15:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek tu

2455
01:15:09,760 --> 01:15:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

2456
01:15:10,460 --> 01:15:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] Onda kaže

2457
01:15:10,840 --> 01:15:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa ostalo imaš

2458
01:15:11,920 --> 01:15:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] parafraziram

2459
01:15:12,920 --> 01:15:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] postoje jedna zemlja

2460
01:15:13,960 --> 01:15:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] koja nije ratovala

2461
01:15:14,779 --> 01:15:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] više od jednog stoljeća.

2462
01:15:16,000 --> 01:15:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] Što su da švicarska?

2463
01:15:16,920 --> 01:15:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] Što su dali?

2464
01:15:17,619 --> 01:15:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] Saca kukavica.

2465
01:15:19,079 --> 01:15:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno to je grozno

2466
01:15:20,840 --> 01:15:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] reći za švicarsku

2467
01:15:21,659 --> 01:15:24,939
[SPEAKER_00] i nije ni istina

2468
01:15:24,939 --> 01:15:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali je uvijek

2469
01:15:26,460 --> 01:15:27,899
[SPEAKER_00] to onako gledano

2470
01:15:27,899 --> 01:15:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] sa pocmijekom.

2471
01:15:29,439 --> 01:15:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] njih baš briga.

2472
01:15:31,680 --> 01:15:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su uredili.

2473
01:15:32,399 --> 01:15:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam razumio

2474
01:15:33,380 --> 01:15:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem značenju

2475
01:15:34,779 --> 01:15:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] Saca kukavicom.

2476
01:15:35,880 --> 01:15:36,899
[SPEAKER_00] Saca kukavicom

2477
01:15:36,899 --> 01:15:37,279
[SPEAKER_00] dakle

2478
01:15:37,279 --> 01:15:38,300
[SPEAKER_00] ideja je

2479
01:15:38,300 --> 01:15:39,520
[SPEAKER_00] koju Orson Welles kaže

2480
01:15:39,520 --> 01:15:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] imate toliko mira

2481
01:15:41,039 --> 01:15:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] a sve što ste napravili

2482
01:15:42,380 --> 01:15:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] sad vaš dosig

2483
01:15:43,239 --> 01:15:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] je Saca kukavicom.

2484
01:15:44,460 --> 01:15:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

2485
01:15:46,119 --> 01:15:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] renesansna Italija

2486
01:15:47,279 --> 01:15:48,100
